summary: This document is an English translation of a lease agreement dated March 21, 2024, between Jiangxi Hualiu (lessor) and Xiamen Pop Network Technology Co., LTD (lessee). The lease is for Unit 304, an office space of 500.91 square meters, located at 168 Fengqi Road, Software Park, Xiamen, for a term of one year from March 21, 2024, to March 20, 2025, at a monthly rent of RMB 12,522.75. The lessee is responsible for additional fees including property management, public maintenance, and utilities, and must provide a performance security deposit of RMB 38,000.
